name: Social Health And Education Development Organization Timarni Samiti
briefDescription: SHEDO is group of energetic and professional youths with strong determination to work for the development of people of society “in a way so that they can help for themselves” through introduce new innovative techniques and methodologies so that the equality and equity can be assured within and between all communities.  SHEDO is officially registered under society registration act 1973 in the year 2014 and since then it started working among the people with a focused objective and a strong determination.
